<taxonomicName id="79A24D27EE49FF9D6B97D19EFCD9F3A2" authority="(Linden &amp; Andre) K. Schum." box="[220,817,222,245]" class="Liliopsida" family="Marantaceae" genus="Monotagma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Zingiberales" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="smaragdinum">
<emphasis id="8CD6EAB6EE49FF9D6B97D19EFE1FF3A2" box="[220,503,222,245]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Monotagma smaragdinum</emphasis>
(Linden &amp; André) K.Schum.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BE1D36A4EE49FF9D6BDCD05EFD87F208" blockId="15.[151,1436,286,467]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Pericarp with 1-layered mesocarp. Seed narrowly cylindrical to narrowly pyramidal; aril tubular without lobes or with two string-shaped straight lobes.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F6B8652FEE49FF9D6B8DD02BFD47F284" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="BE1D36A4EE49FF9D6B8DD02BFD47F284" blockId="15.[151,1436,286,467]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
<emphasis id="8CD6EAB6EE49FF9D6B8DD02BFEA2F2D2" bold="true" box="[198,330,363,389]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Discussion</emphasis>
:— 
<taxonomicName id="79A24D27EE49FF9D6A24D02CFD5BF2D2" box="[367,691,364,390]" class="Liliopsida" family="Marantaceae" genus="Monotagma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Zingiberales" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Tubularia">
<emphasis id="8CD6EAB6EE49FF9D6A24D02CFE14F2D2" box="[367,508,364,389]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Monotagma</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis id="8CD6EAB6EE49FF9D690BD02CFD5BF2D2" box="[576,691,364,389]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Tubularia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comprises 17 species. It is characterized by having fruits with a one-layered mesocarp with unsclerified cells, and tubular arils with laterally united lobes. These features are apomorphic for this section (
<bibRefCitation id="DA334B55EE49FF9D6AACD0F9FD4BF284" author="Hagberg, M." box="[487,675,441,467]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refId="ref20101" refString="Hagberg, M. (1990 b) The genus Monotagma (Marantaceae). Unpublished Ph. D. dissertation, Department of Systematic Botany, University of Gothenburg, 90 pp." type="book" year="1990">Hagberg 1990b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
